# STEP 1 — Update Layout Structure

Open **App.tsx**

Find this part:

```tsx
<div className="body">
  <div className="container">
```

### CHANGE it to

```tsx
<div className="app">

  <div className="sidebar">
    <h2>Chats</h2>

    <button>+ New Chat</button>

    <div className="chatList">
      <p>Chat 1</p>
      <p>Chat 2</p>
      <p>Chat 3</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div className="container">
```

Now your layout has **2 sections**:

```
Sidebar
Chat Window
```

---

# STEP 2 — Update CSS Layout

Add these styles to **App.css**.

```css
.app{
  display:flex;
  height:100vh;
}

/* Sidebar */

.sidebar{
  width:220px;
  background:#202123;
  color:white;
  padding:15px;
}

.sidebar button{
  width:100%;
  margin:10px 0;
  padding:8px;
}

.chatList p{
  padding:8px;
  border-radius:5px;
  cursor:pointer;
}

.chatList p:hover{
  background:#343541;
}

/* Chat area */

.container{
  flex:1;
  padding:20px;
}
```

---

# STEP 3 — Adjust Body CSS

Remove the **center alignment** from `.body` because now we have a sidebar.

Delete this section if it exists:

```css
.body{
  width:100%;
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
}
```

